lead_paragraph: Free agent Eric Thames agreed Tuesday to a $16 million, three-year contract with the Milwaukee Brewers, who cut first baseman Chris Carter after a 41-homer season that tied for the National League lead.

headline.print_headline: Eric Thames Joins Brewers, Who Cut Chris Carter
